---
title: Chermoula Lamb Tacos with Greek Salad & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Greek salad in a taco? Yep, we did it. This fancy feast is as outrageous as it sounds, but only in the best way possible. Featuring succulent Moroccan-spiced lamb, a Mediterranean salad with crumbly feta and a drizzle of lemon yoghurt,  all wrapped up in a soft tortilla. Tempted for a taste yet?
